These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, juice
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, malaysian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the malaysian##1
2. the malaysian is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | juice     | mirinda |
| Nationality   | malaysian | pakistani      |
| Sport         | water-polo    | volleyball      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, drama
2 different pets are kept: lizard, bird
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Hobby         | drawing      | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | action    |
| Pet           | bird         | lizard         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, freelancer
2 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the chef is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Job         | chef | freelancer |
| Pet         | hedgehog       | ferret       |
| Transport   | trike       | skateboard         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
