The people have 2 different hobbies: woodworking, chess
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, subway
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage    | lemonade    | hot-chocolate     |
| Hobby       | woodworking    | chess |
| Transport   | motorbike | subway    |

